Description:Test puzzle for replaying an infinite combat loop with Sword of Hearth and Home on a token plus Aurelia, the Warleader. Attack with Aurelia and the equipped Spirit token. Sword of Hearth and Home should blink Aurelia, resetting her first-attack trigger for the next combat. Record one combat cycle and repeat until the opponent is defeated.

